<p><a href="https://www.npr.org/podcasts/510313/how-i-built-this" target="_blank" rel="noopener">This NPR podcast</a> consists of interviews with experienced startup founders who explain how they got where they are. Itâ€™s not solely focused on tech, but more around how people built their business from the ground up. They have several tech episodes that I truly recommend:</p>
